    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that there are different views, but some people say that calling it a \"debate\" is kind of a way to avoid saying that healthcare *is* a human right, like it's just an objective fact in modern ethics. don't you think the \"government takeover\" argument is just an excuse to keep things as they are?",
